{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/how-to-take-screenshots-from-chrome-51kj/","result":{"data":{"devArticles":{"article":{"title":"üì∏ How To Take Screenshots From Chrome","slug":"how-to-take-screenshots-from-chrome-51kj","description":"There are lots of Chrome extensions are available to take screenshots of websites.  But you know you...","tags":["productivity","chrome","webdev"],"readable_publish_date":"Feb 21 '20","body_html":"<p>There are lots of Chrome extensions are available to take screenshots of websites.</p>\n\n<p>But you know you can use Chrome's device toolbar to take screenshots of a website in any device sizes?</p>\n\n<h3>\n  <a name=\"1-go-to-website\" href=\"#1-go-to-website\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  1. Go to Website\n</h3>\n\n<h3>\n  <a name=\"2-open-developer-tools\" href=\"#2-open-developer-tools\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  2. Open Developer Tools\n</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--VV2dSsfw--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/l1uw9szar62e6o9nz27q.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--VV2dSsfw--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/l1uw9szar62e6o9nz27q.png\" alt=\"Open Developer Tools\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n\n<h3>\n  <a name=\"3-click-toggle-device-toolbar-option\" href=\"#3-click-toggle-device-toolbar-option\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  3. Click Toggle Device Toolbar Option\n</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--D8bLcFjD--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/14fe9seqxv4otp9eazcy.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--D8bLcFjD--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/14fe9seqxv4otp9eazcy.png\" alt=\"Device Toolbar Option\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n\n<h3>\n  <a name=\"4-choose-screen-size\" href=\"#4-choose-screen-size\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  4. Choose Screen Size\n</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--N7iORBEe--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/jhn8jf09g177k2xm7zs1.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--N7iORBEe--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/jhn8jf09g177k2xm7zs1.png\" alt=\"Screen Size\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n\n<p>Or you can choose the Responsive option and adjust the size.</p>\n\n<h3>\n  <a name=\"5-click-menu-icon\" href=\"#5-click-menu-icon\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  5. Click Menu Icon\n</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--ZcH_4xFS--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/j65f3ze32o8jol3hqpll.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--ZcH_4xFS--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/j65f3ze32o8jol3hqpll.png\" alt=\"Menu Icon\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n\n<h3>\n  <a name=\"6-choose-capture-screenshot-option\" href=\"#6-choose-capture-screenshot-option\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  6. Choose Capture Screenshot Option\n</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--R5y45Kc7--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/zt889y96yrnu1yeaz9lh.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--R5y45Kc7--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/i/zt889y96yrnu1yeaz9lh.png\" alt=\"Capture Screenshot\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n\n<h1>\n  <a name=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  ‚úåÔ∏è\n</h1>\n\n","url":"https://dev.to/ctrleffive/how-to-take-screenshots-from-chrome-51kj","cover_image":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"how-to-take-screenshots-from-chrome-51kj"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1617812919"]}